incite fears of espionage by unnamed american leaders uninterested 
in improving ussoviet relations 
were not the ones who initiated this process gerasimov 
said tacitly acknowledging the connection between last weeks 
incident and the expulsion of van gundy 
using almost the same words gilbert used to denounce todays 
action gerasimov called the expulsion of pakhtusov a provocation 
