helicopters and a light airplane as well as at least one speedboat 
the foreign ministers of the five nations will ask the united 
nations to begin setting up the peacekeeping force a step tinoco 
called a formality 
in february the foreign ministers agreed in principle that un 
military observers should operate in the region to verify reports of 
guerrilla activity and by their presence deter such raids 
the united nations then drafted a plan calling for up to 100 
