the sale of eastern airlines is an increasingly 
likely option for parent texas air corp as the crippling strike 
against the carrier continues with no sign of resolution experts 
said wednesday 
on the 12th day of a bitter strike by easterns machinists union 
the airline still was operating only a fraction of its normal 
